Class BaseTDepartmentBean

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.aurel.track.beans.base.BaseTDepartmentBean
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    TDepartmentBean

    public abstract class BaseTDepartmentBean
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    This table holds the departments. Each user belongs to one department. You should not use this class directly. It should not even be extended; all references should be to TDepartmentBean
